headline: Textron Aviation Expands Affordable and Convenient Health Care Options for Wichita Employees With Second Onsite Plane Healthy Wellness Center & Pharmacy
summary: WICHITA, Kan., April 08, 2025--Textron Aviation announced the opening of second Plane Healthy Wellness Center & Pharmacy, located at company’s east headquarters in Wichita, Kansas.

headline: Textron Aviation European Distribution Center Celebrates 10 Years as It Grows Cessna and Beechcraft Parts Availability in Region
summary: DÜSSELDORF, Germany, April 08, 2025--Textron Aviation's European Distribution Center celebrates 10 years of proudly serving customers with parts support in Europe and APAC.
